%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%

sequenceDiagram
autonumber

actor PM as Program Manager
participant UI as Innovation UI
participant BFF as Innovation BFF
participant SERVICE as Innovation Service
participant OPENTEXT as MSIL OpenText DMS
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS Read schema"}
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}
participant NS as Notification Service

PM ->> UI: Click Startup (open preview)
UI ->> BFF: getStartupPreview(startupId)

BFF ->> SERVICE: fetchStartupPreview(startupId)
SERVICE ->> READDB: Get startup details, stage timeline, documents, comments
READDB -->> SERVICE: Preview data
SERVICE -->> BFF: Preview response
BFF -->> UI: Render startup preview

alt Upload Document
    PM ->> UI: Upload document
    UI ->> BFF: uploadDocument(file)
    BFF ->> OPENTEXT: Store file
    OPENTEXT -->> BFF: document_id
    BFF ->> SERVICE: saveDocumentMetadata(startupId, document_id)
    SERVICE ->> PRIMARYDB: INSERT document metadata
    SERVICE ->> KAFKA: Publish DocumentUploaded
    KAFKA ->> NS: Notify stakeholders
    SERVICE -->> BFF: Upload success
    BFF -->> UI: Refresh document list
else Add Comment / Request Document
    PM ->> UI: Add comment / request
    UI ->> BFF: addComment(startupId, text)
    BFF ->> SERVICE: saveComment()
    SERVICE ->> PRIMARYDB: INSERT comment
    SERVICE ->> KAFKA: Publish CommentAdded
    KAFKA ->> NS: Notify Startup
    SERVICE -->> BFF: Comment saved
    BFF -->> UI: Refresh comment history
end